  "text": "We employ tree grafting and direction-optimized BFS [CITATION_1] to the MS-BFS algorithm and call it the MS-BFS-Graft algorithm. A multithreaded version of this algorithm is described in Algorithm 3 that takes a bipartite graph GðX [ Y; EÞ and an initial matching represented by a mate array of size jX [ Y j as inputs. mate½u is set to -1 for an unmatched vertex u. The MS-BFS-Graft algorithm updates the mate array with the maximum cardinality matching. for",
